deprecated

additionally want to add setter methods for changing deadline and event
times

previously chatbot identified tasks from whether it contains key words
such as /by and /from

now chatbot checks first word to identify command to follow standards in
instructions

Modified runtest.bat file to include correct file path

added input commands into input.txt and expected output into EXPECTED.TXT

Run runtest.bat to test

Currently Many classes were located in a single .java file, this makes reading code difficult

Hence Classes were separated into their individual filed

current code had magic numbers, redundant print statments, and non descriptive method names

changed magic numbers and reused Strings into constants, changed several method nammes to verbs that properly describe function
